name: Chiffon
detail: Our Chiffon is a plain-woven fabric that is breathable, soft, and flowy. This airy Chiffon is made of 100% Polyester and has a slightly translucent top layer of fabric. We double line these pieces to give you comfort and elegance. This is a lightweight fabric that has minimal stretch and can be worn any time of year.

name: Tulle
detail: Our Tulle is a lightweight hexagonal woven fabric, made of 100% polyester fibers. This soft Tulle is always double lined with a proper dyed to match lining, so your colors are always unison to one another. Our Tulle does not carry an elastane meaning there is no stretch, but not to worry as this fabric is used to create our soft, delicate, and flowy silhouettes.

name: Sequin
detail: Sequin bridesmaid dresses are sparkling options that provide glamour and glitter. They are one of the latest trends that can be worn all year and mix-and-match with different fabrics. Sequin dresses offer a combination of elegance, traditional styles, and classic looks in one. Adding sequins to your bridesmaids’ styles will make your wedding colors pop and stand out. We have a selection of dresses, pants, skirts, and tops to choose from. Our styles can come in silver, champagne gold, rose gold, gold, cabernet, matte rose gold, navy blue, charcoal, black, and emerald. Try on our sequin bridesmaid dresses at home now! We ship them right to your door.
